==================================
[ K A L I K I B Z ] - Wireless Internet Provider
==================================

Select Data Package:
1. 1 Hour Unlimited - Ksh 10
2. 6 Hours Unlimited - Ksh 20 
3. 12 Hours Unlimited - Ksh 30
4. 24 Hours Unlimited - Ksh 40

Enter option (1-4): [INPUT]

PAYMENT PROCESSING
Enter Kenyan Phone Number: [INPUT]

[SUBMIT BUTTON]

<<SYSTEM FUNCTIONALITY>>
- Validates phone number format (07XXXXXXXX)
- Triggers mobile money prompt via:
   * M-Pesa STK Push (if Safaricom)
   * Airtel Money (if Airtel)
- Payment automatically routed to 0740888135
- Sends confirmation SMS to user
- Grants WAN access via your router for duration:
   1. Creates timed firewall rule (1/6/12/24hrs)
   2. Maps device MAC/IP to allowed list
   3. Automatic disconnection after expiry

[ROUTER INTEGRATION]
- Uses cron jobs/API to:
   - Reset bandwidth counters periodically
   - Sync with PPPoE authentication
   - Monitor connected devices
   - Log all transactions

[SECURITY FEATURES]
- TLS encryption for payments
- Rate limiting
- IP/MAC binding
- Fraud detection system

[ADMIN DASHBOARD]
- Real-time users monitor
- Payment records
- Network health stats
- Package configuration

<<USER INSTRUCTIONS>>
1. Connect to "kalikibz" WiFi
2. Launch portal -> Select package
3. Complete mobile payment
4. Instant internet access

<<DISCLAIMER>>
This software requires:
- Python/Node.js backend
- MySQL database
- RouterOS API integration
- Mobile money API licenses
- Proper cybersecurity implementatio
